    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1892-08-20T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1892-08-20T00:00:00-05:00" n="241" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d241">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Herbert</persName> to Mr.
                                    <persName type="to">Foster</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">British
                                        Legation</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">New
                                    York</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1892-08-20">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 20,
                                1892</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Much regret to say have missed connection, owing to hot box, and can not
                            be in Washington till 2; if not inconvenient to you might I follow you
                            to-morrow or next day?</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Herbert.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
